data.text: @SteveWestly Except that so many already eligible cannot even make an appointment.  At least not in NJ.  Nothing available on any of the myriad sites.  It's the Hunger Games of vaccines.

@SteveWestly @KPMemberService has administered 260,000 vaccine doses in California to date. They employ 218,000 in the state. So of their 12.4mm members in CA, rough math says they’ve vaccinated 0.3% of their members. I thought they’d have leverage? Not so much
